<page>
  <heading>Release notes</heading>

  <content>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0">
      <b>The 2.1.1 Release of Carrot<sup>2</sup></b> brings a number of new
      features and bugfixes.
    </p>

    <table class="release-notes">
      <tr>
        <td class="head">Clustering by site and source</td>

        <td>
          The 2.1.1 release of <c2 /> adds two more options for clustering.
          Apart from the traditional "by-topic" grouping, now also "by-source"
          and "by-site" options are available.

          <img class="pic rn" src="img/release-2.1.1/facet-tabs.gif" alt="By Topic and By Source clustering" />
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">Solr input configuration dialog</td>

        <td>
          A configuration dialog for the Solr input is now available in the GUI
          Tuning Browser (<a href="http://issues.carrot2.org/browse/CARROT-109">CARROT-109</a>).

          <img class="pic rn" src="img/release-2.1.1/solr-config.gif" alt="Solr input configuration dialog" />
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">Multithreaded benchmarking</td>

        <td>
          Clustering algorithm benchmarks in the GUI Tuning Browser can be now run
          in a multithreaded mode (<a href="http://issues.carrot2.org/browse/CARROT-111">CARROT-111</a>).

          <img class="pic rn" src="img/release-2.1.1/benchmark-threads.gif" alt="Multithreaded benchmarking" />
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">Beta label on the web application from HEAD</td>

        <td>
          The web application built from HEAD has now a "beta" mark near the logo
          (<a href="http://issues.carrot2.org/browse/CARROT-115">CARROT-115</a>).

          <a href="http://demo.carrot2.org/demo-head/">
          <img class="pic rn" src="img/release-2.1.1/webapp-beta.gif" alt="Beta mark on the web application from HEAD" /></a>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">Other improvemetns</td>

        <td>
          For other bug fixes and improvements, please see the <a
          href="http://issues.carrot2.org/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;styleName=Html&amp;version=10030">JIRA
          Release Notes</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </content>
</page>
